WEBVTT

00:00:12.283 --> 00:00:21.792 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Jehovah, dear Father,
There seemed no hope for us.

00:00:21.792 --> 00:00:30.926 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
The ransom has given
Hope to ev’ryone!

00:00:30.926 --> 00:00:40.227 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
We give our lives to you,
Our best in all we do.

00:00:40.227 --> 00:00:48.736 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
And we’ll tell others too,
That your will might be done.

00:00:48.736 --> 00:00:57.870 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
You gave your precious Son,
And now we sing as one,

00:00:57.870 --> 00:01:09.882 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
A song we’ll sing forever,
for giving us your precious Son.

00:01:12.217 --> 00:01:20.935 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Your kindness, your mercy,
They draw us close to you.

00:01:20.935 --> 00:01:29.735 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Your great name, your friendship,
These we’ve come to love.

00:01:29.735 --> 00:01:38.619 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
But something more than this
Is your most precious gift.

00:01:38.619 --> 00:01:46.543 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
He died that we might live.
You sent him from above.

00:01:46.543 --> 00:01:55.678 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
You gave your precious Son,
And now we sing as one,

00:01:55.678 --> 00:02:10.109 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
A song we’ll sing forever,
for giving us your precious Son—

00:02:10.109 --> 00:02:16.365 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
for giving us your precious Son.

00:02:16.365 --> 00:02:25.290 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Jehovah, dear Father,
we pray in gratitude.

00:02:25.290 --> 00:02:37.928 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
We offer our thanks
for giving us your precious Son.

